title: Citrix Controller Sessions
agents: windows
catalog: app/citrix
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the active and inactive sessions of Citrix XenApp 7.x controllers.
 The citrix_farm.ps1 plugin must be installed on the controller, and
 the Check_MK agent must be executed with Citrix Admin permissions
 for this to work. The check allows to set upper levels on active, inactive and total
 sessions. Defaults are not set.

inventory:
 One service per controller is created.

